{
  "stem": "3666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, we had to get up, and it was called an appell, like roll calling.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, you had to, like, really look straight at the person who was counting the rows.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe I, as a kid, I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kind of turned my head to the side, and suddenly I felt such a blow right here in my left side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember seeing my head falling on the floor and coming back up, down and up, until it diminished, but it was-- I thought-- I thought that he knocked off my head.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't faint, no, but I was not aware of where I was and what happened to me for a good few seconds, maybe more than just a few seconds.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And actually, I had suffered from that blow was something very serious because eight years ago, I had a tumor removed, called meningioma, from my brain over here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the doctor asked me immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you ever get hit here, because this particular tumor is prevalent among construction workers who get hit, something falls on your head.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, well, it looks like it was there from the war, and it just took many years to grow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I almost died from that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it wasn't malignant?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not malignant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a tumor the size of a plum, growing and pressing on my brain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, like, a half an inch from my optic nerve.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And eight years ago, it was removed, and I'm very, very lucky that I'm alive and that I'm well coordinated also.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I mean, physically, my motor skills.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
